  ⚠ unicorn(no-confusing-array-with): Avoid using a negative index with `Array#with()`.
   ╭─[no_confusing_array_with.tsx:1:7]
 1 │ array.with(-1, value)
   ·       ────
   ╰────
  help: Use a non-negative index to make the intended position explicit.
  note: `Array#with()` interprets a negative index as an offset from the end.

